t&#8217;s efficient, producing papers at a much lower cost that traditional=
 scientific research processes.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The AI Scientist follo=
ws a three-step process for conducting scientific research:</p><ul style=3D=
"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special=
