); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding=
-left: 4px;"><strong>Idea Generation: </strong><span>Brainstorms and propos=
es novel research directions, and searches existing literature to ensure th=
e novelty of its ideas.</span></p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; m=
so-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(=
