0; padding-left: 4px;"><strong>Experimentation:</strong><span> Implements t=
he proposed ideas, executes experiments, and generates results. It then vis=
ualizes these results, creating plots and notes for further analysis.</span=
></p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><=
