g>Papering: </strong><span>Writes a research paper using the data from its =
experiments, in a standard scientific format. It then undergoes AI-powered =
reviews that have near human accuracy. Finally, it uses the feedback from t=
he reviews to improve its ideas and experimentations.</span></p></li></ul><=
p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; marg=
in: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Voil&#224;, we have a scientist! And it&#8217;s actu=
