?</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px=
; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">At this point it&#8217;s relatively obvious that Oze=
mpic works in treating obesity. Patients can expect to lose 5-15% of their =
body weight over the course of several months. It&#8217;s an effective and,=
 from what we can tell, safe weight loss treatment that works on almost eve=
ry body that takes it.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>But as we&#8217;ve pointe=
d out multiple times in the </span><em>Weekly Dose, </em><span>Ozempic (and=
